    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Truth Seekers is a class-based immersive horror multiplayer cooperative shooter game that throws players into the heart of environments where urban legends and folklore monsters reside. Join forces with your friends to track down and confront the legendary Bigfoot, and the elusive Stagwalker. Teamwork and strategy are key as you and your team navigate through dangerous encounters. Be careful as you decide whether to stick together or split up; the wrong choice could lead to the gruesome death of a hunter. To ensure smooth coordination, someone must take charge back at the RV, monitoring players' movements and surveillance cameras to call the shots and keep players informed of their surroundings. Do you have what it takes to hunt these urban legends?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/c11ec194785642591b33f49240bd5852.poster.avif?t=1768157831\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/c11ec194785642591b33f49240bd5852.webm?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/c11ec194785642591b33f49240bd5852.mp4?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CAPTURE THE PROOF</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove to the world that these urban legends are more than just myths—the truth is out there…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/afb678cfcaf5fc16abbdef935322ec68.poster.avif?t=1768157831\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/afb678cfcaf5fc16abbdef935322ec68.webm?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/afb678cfcaf5fc16abbdef935322ec68.mp4?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMMUNICATE BY ANY MEANS POSSIBLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are &quot;dead zones&quot; located throughout, which disable long-range communication with the walkie-talkie. Stay in touch by any means necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/b28726dccd6ad6f45c239ec7b3a5e01b.poster.avif?t=1768157831\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/b28726dccd6ad6f45c239ec7b3a5e01b.webm?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/b28726dccd6ad6f45c239ec7b3a5e01b.mp4?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT AND FIND GEAR UPGRADES TO AID IN YOUR HUNT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and craft weapons, medicinal supplies, alcohol, drugs, and other resources to aid in your hunt against these monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/a168bc630e0b52cd1dbca817d137baa2.poster.avif?t=1768157831\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/a168bc630e0b52cd1dbca817d137baa2.webm?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/a168bc630e0b52cd1dbca817d137baa2.mp4?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORK TOGETHER, OR IT COULD SPELL DEATH</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Splitting up can be dangerous, but sometimes is necessary. Will you risk it? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/d3c8499941ea4ffbcee7fa0facab994b.poster.avif?t=1768157831\" width=576 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/d3c8499941ea4ffbcee7fa0facab994b.webm?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276780/extras/d3c8499941ea4ffbcee7fa0facab994b.mp4?t=1768157831\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIND ALTERING SUBSTANCES HELP REDUCE THE PAIN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share a beer with your friends or indulge in the forest's natural mushrooms, which can be found throughout. They restore your health, but is it worth the price?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >___________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>FEATURES:</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• 2 maps to hunt with varying difficulty and size, as well as monsters.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Advanced, blood thirsty AI that wants you dead.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Full multiplayer cooperative experience up to 3 players.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Crafting and looting.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• 3</strong> <strong>character classes to play as: The Hunter, The Tracker, and The Camera Guy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• And much, much more...</strong></p>",
